                        <ul>
                            <li>AP courses in every high school via distance learning</li>
                            <li>SAT/ACT prep free for all students</li>
                            <li>Guaranteed college admission for top 10% of every school</li>
                            <li>Full rides to state schools for family income under $65,000</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                
